{"tid":1908977,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肺炎肆虐 中國婦人情急智生將鈔票放微波爐消毒 總數$3,482歷時1分鐘即「化灰」！","createTime":"2020-03-03T15:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T15:58:27.000Z","uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ac9ee392cb9c372ed015cf39ea5197cf6a6ca2","tid":1908977,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37da3f0810ae923896eea91ec045228f5a566782","tid":1908977,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:46:02.000Z","msg":"車厘龜呢?"},{"pid":"f10fede54a6b3580a5f7583d12317678c5fd13f0","tid":1908977,"uid":44978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:46:08.000Z","msg":"支那人唔係唔用現金既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c814d114647c947849745c970f3c52d5488df95","tid":1908977,"uid":63113,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ATAVxp0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FATAVxp0.png&h=969b4e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎（武漢肺炎）疫情肆虐，內地有人因怕鈔票帶有病毒，竟心生一計將之放入微波爐消毒，結果令鈔票全數「炭化」報銷，幸有銀行願意代為點算退換才不致血本無歸。銀行指疫情發生後，已加強為鈔票消毒清潔，著市民毋須擔心。<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情蔓延，市民特別注重衛生，其中流傳度高的鈔票就令人憂慮會成為病毒傳播途徑。據《環球網》報道於2月中下旬，江蘇無錫一名姓李老婦就因擔心鈔票不潔，故將一疊鈔票放入微波爐加熱「消毒」，結果不到一分鐘已傳出異味，她發現大事不妙將鈔票取出時經已太遲。<br />\n<br />\n微波爐叮銀紙致炭化 銀行逐張點算全額退還<br />\n<br />\n因鈔票大部分位置已呈現焦黑炭化，肯定無法繼續使用。老婦情急之下立即帶同鈔票往銀行諮詢，惟有銀行要求她出示鈔票遭火燒的證明，令她幾近絕望。<br />\n<br />\n幸而其中一間銀行得悉事件後，會計部經理願意遵照規定，儘量為李女彌補損失。但由於鈔票損毀嚴重，稍為用力擠壓已經會碎裂「化灰」，令職員點只能以人手逐張鈔票確認真偽，足足花了一整個下午才點算出總額為3,125元人民幣（約$3,482港元），並為李女更換全額新鈔。<br />\n<br />\n銀紙經消毒 放置2周再推出市面<br />\n<br />\n該銀行負責人表示，自疫情發生後各監管部分已相當重視流動貨幣消毒。除新鈔以外，所有回籠現金都要經過紫外線或高溫消毒，而且一般會放置14天以上才會再流出市民，故認為從銀行流出的鈔票都是「乾淨錢」，民眾毋須擔心。"},{"pid":"08bce454fe438e8fc2b0d533dc978fd3f42ba5d2","tid":1908977,"uid":4519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"人地富戶燒真衣紙姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67155e19512a745f176dece6d3bf70f4cd93b718","tid":1908977,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:47:14.000Z","msg":"叮埋電話呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99718c32c3a8d0c93c2c1561dc8b00f9dc026c8a","tid":1908977,"uid":63113,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"08bce454fe438e8fc2b0d533dc978fd3f42ba5d2","tid":1908977,"uid":4519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"人地富戶燒真衣紙姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2va5LP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2va5LP.gif&h=6d9c5334&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"266ea85d4f2e00ec090a61aac1f2b525a12a7fd0","tid":1908977,"uid":78039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:49:12.000Z","msg":"識得微波消毒其實都叻丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ac174660f635bcc4b41787e99503864acdfce9","tid":1908977,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99718c32c3a8d0c93c2c1561dc8b00f9dc026c8a","tid":1908977,"uid":63113,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"08bce454fe438e8fc2b0d533dc978fd3f42ba5d2","tid":1908977,"uid":4519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"人地富戶燒真衣紙姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2va5LP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2va5LP.gif&h=6d9c5334&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face